channel.title: New account
channel.description:
Just made a new account and didn't spend much time leveling up some skills, but I made the account a member since I really haven't experienced that form of the game yet.
Best ways to level up quickly and make good money with a new account?
Levels include 20 attack, 30 strength, 14 defence, 35 mage, 21 range, 39 mining, 40 fishing, 40 cooking, and 40 woodcutting. Oh, and 30 hp (lol @ fail stats)
But yeah, any suggestion would be appreciated.
